Actor Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson and Lauren Hashian arrive for the Premiere Of Columbia Pictures' "Jumanji: Welcome To The Jungle" held at The TLC Chinese Theater on December 11, 2017 in Hollywood, California. JOHANNESBURG - Dwayne "The Rock" Johnson announced that he has married long-time girlfriend Lauren Hashian. Johnson posted a picture on his Instagram account on Monday showing the couple standing on a rise which overlooks an ocean in Hawaii, with the caption: "We do. August 18th, 2019. Hawaii. Pōmaikaʻi (blessed)." The couple reportedly met in 2006 and started dating following his divorce from producer Dany Garcia. Johnson and Hashian are the parents of two daughters. We do.  August 18th, 2019. Hawaii. Pōmaikaʻi (blessed)  @laurenhashianofficial❤️ @hhgarcia41📸 A post shared by  therock (@therock) on Aug 19, 2019 at 3:27am PDT